import React from 'react';
import {
  Container,
  Typography,
  Box,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  Grid,
  Button,
  LinearProgress,
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  Restaurant,
  Add,
  LocalFireDepartment,
  FitnessCenter,
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const Nutrition: React.FC = () => {
  const nutritionStats = [
    { label: 'Calories', current: 1250, target: 2000, unit: 'kcal', color: 'primary' },
    { label: 'Protein', current: 85, target: 140, unit: 'g', color: 'secondary' },
    { label: 'Carbs', current: 150, target: 250, unit: 'g', color: 'success' },
    { label: 'Fat', current: 45, target: 67, unit: 'g', color: 'warning' },
  ];

  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg">
      <Box sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom>
          Nutrition Tracker
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
          Track your daily nutrition and reach your goals
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      {/* Daily Overview */}
      <Grid container spacing={3} sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        {nutritionStats.map((stat, index) => (
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3} key={index}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  {stat.label}
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="h4" color={`${stat.color}.main`} gutterBottom>
                  {stat.current}
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                  of {stat.target} {stat.unit}
                </Typography>
                <LinearProgress
                  variant="determinate"
                  value={(stat.current / stat.target) * 100}
                  color={stat.color as any}
                />
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>

      {/* Quick Actions */}
      <Grid container spacing={3} sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center', py: 4 }}>
              <Add sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: 'primary.main', mb: 2 }} />
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Log Food
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                Add meals and snacks to track your nutrition
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="contained" size="large">
                Add Food
              </Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center', py: 4 }}>
              <Restaurant sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: 'secondary.main', mb: 2 }} />
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Meal Plans
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                Browse recommended meal plans for your goals
              </Typography>
              <Button variant="outlined" size="large">
                View Plans
              </Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

      {/* Recent Meals */}
      <Card>
        <CardContent>
          <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
            Today's Meals
          </Typography>
          <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', py: 4 }}>
            <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
              No meals logged yet today
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
              Start by adding your breakfast!
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Nutrition;
